":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:41:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>報左HKU BA music (non-jupas)<br />\n有冇人做過份written test<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我冇做過 <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">不過有份改過</span></span><br />\n主要考五級樂理知識 可能要你默譜<br />\n聽tape辨別中西樂器<br />\n最好對中西音樂史有基礎知識<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">其實interview至係關鍵</span></span><br />\n反而建議樓主諗清楚自己有幾想入呢個 department <br />\n如果你只係想要港大個名 呢度好歡迎你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係 請唔好對呢度期望過高 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高分先有interview機會?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34e56fcbea50437bfa68eaa0e7b2e837d32fc7b","tid":199500,"uid":103434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T19:10:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>報左HKU BA music (non-jupas)<br />\n有冇人做過份written test<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我冇做過 <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">不過有份改過</span></span><br />\n主要考五級樂理知識 可能要你默譜<br />\n聽tape辨別中西樂器<br />\n最好對中西音樂史有基礎知識<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">其實interview至係關鍵</span></span><br />\n反而建議樓主諗清楚自己有幾想入呢個 department <br />\n如果你只係想要港大個名 呢度好歡迎你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係 請唔好對呢度期望過高 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高分先有interview機會?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n高分你指aptitude test定你個sub-degree / first degree成績?<br />\n其實份test表現正正常常就應該有得shortlist interview嘅<br />\n不過實質點揀人就唔清楚<br />\n而且要記住specialist scheme唔會直接出offer<br />\n而係推薦俾faculty of arts, faculty先有最後決定權<br />\n<br />\nOn top of that, 想知樓主點解會有興趣報HKU music? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808ee916e27cfe6c5ddcd46b23860731f11ddee0","tid":199500,"uid":103434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T19:12:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>報左HKU BA music (non-jupas)<br />\n有冇人做過份written test<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我冇做過 <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">不過有份改過</span></span><br />\n主要考五級樂理知識 可能要你默譜<br />\n聽tape辨別中西樂器<br />\n最好對中西音樂史有基礎知識<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">其實interview至係關鍵</span></span><br />\n反而建議樓主諗清楚自己有幾想入呢個 department <br />\n如果你只係想要港大個名 呢度好歡迎你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係 請唔好對呢度期望過高 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高分先有interview機會?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n高分你指aptitude test定你個sub-degree / first degree成績?<br />\n其實份test表現正正常常就應該有得shortlist interview嘅<br />\n不過實質點揀人就唔清楚<br />\n而且要記住specialist scheme唔會直接出offer<br />\n而係推薦俾faculty of arts, faculty先有最後決定權<br />\n<br />\nOn top of that, 想知樓主點解會有興趣報HKU music? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果想私底下傾 可以email我：8yb5a (at) boun.cr"}]}